<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c1">" واهٍ"</span>. <span class="c1">"الدراية"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ١٣٩)</span>. <span class="c1">"متروك"</span>. <span class="c1">"المهرة"</span> <span class="c2">(٩/ ٢٦١)</span>، و<span class="c1">"التلخيص"</span> <span class="c2">(٣/ ١٥٢، ١٧٣)</span>، و<span class="c1">"المطالب"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ١٠٣)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c1">"متهم بالكذب"</span>. <span class="c1">"اللسان"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٥٧٢)</span>.<span class="c5"> ترجمة:</span> الحسين بن محمد بن عباد.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
